2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of uncertainty measures and prediction quality rating, which are important topics in machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the use of neural networks for image segmentation. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of entropy as a pixel-wise uncertainty measure. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with the use of neural networks for image segmentation and uncertainty estimation.
